  "consentDialogBody": "This app communicates with the following sites to fetch novels. Following ADR-0001 / ADR-0003, it performs active caching (only works the user selects \"Add to Library\") and respects each site's rate limits (Kakuyomu: 1 req / 2 s) and robots.txt.\n\nKakuyomu content is fetched by parsing HTML. Fetching may fail if the site structure changes.",
